### Create address
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/addresses
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token=PASTE_TOKEN

{
  "label": "Home",
  "line1": "123 Main St",
  "city": "City",
  "state": "State",
  "zip": "12345",
  "isDefault": true
}

### Get addresses
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/addresses
Cookie: token=PASTE_TOKEN

### Update address
PUT http://localhost:4000/auth/addresses/PASTE_ADDRESS_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token=PASTE_TOKEN

{
  "label": "Work",
  "isDefault": false
}

### Delete address
DELETE http://localhost:4000/auth/addresses/PASTE_ADDRESS_ID
Cookie: token=PASTE_TOKEN
